      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The building trades committee met\nlast night at Central Labor hall to\nconsider the deman OF the building\nlaborers for a raise in the wage scale,\nThe committee did not. as was ex-\npected. arrive at any definite decision,\nbut II is probable that they will\nrecommend the trades council to en-\ndorse the unions petition."
